OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of fraud
OL,4,Cafter raids at funeral homes
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested after
OL,7,Ftwo funeral homes in Lancashire were
OL,8,Fraided by police.
OL,10,FOfficers raided two Martin's Funeral
OL,11,FDirectors properties in Preston and
OL,12,FLongridge on the morning of 28 April.
OL,14,FPolice say a man in his 60s and a
OL,15,Fwoman in her 50s, both from Preston,
OL,16,Fhave been arrested on suspicion of
OL,17,Ffraud by false representation.
OL,19,FThey remain in custody for questioning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
