OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777389066
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of fraud
OL,4,Cafter raids at funeral homes
OL,6,FLancashire Constabulary said the raids
OL,7,Fcome after they were contacted in
OL,8,FApril 2026 "in relation to concerns
OL,9,Fabout some of the practices at
OL,10,FMartin's Funeral Directors".
OL,12,FThe raids took place in Tulketh Brow
OL,13,Fin Ashton-on-Ribble and Stonebridge
OL,14,FParade in Longridge.
OL,16,FOfficers have also carried out
OL,17,Fsearches of a private address in The
OL,18,FFriars in Fulwood.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
