FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777389066
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of fraud
OL,4,Cafter raids at funeral homes
OL,6,FThe force said: "Officers have carried
OL,7,Fout thorough searches of the
OL,8,Faddresses, accompanied by a public
OL,9,Fhealth inspector, and we have not
OL,10,Ffound anything untoward in respect of
OL,11,Fthe treatment or storage of peoples'
OL,12,Floved ones.
OL,14,F"Our investigation is continuing but
OL,15,Fis focussed solely on potential
OL,16,Ffinancial irregularities relating to
OL,17,Fthe business.
OL,19,F"Our ongoing enquiries will not impact
OL,20,Fon the business continuing to provide
OL,21,Ffuneral services at this time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
